{"tid":1128844,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[行山]釣魚翁冇魚釣","createTime":"2019-04-28T06:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T07:09:22.000Z","uid":64601,"like":23,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7bd18cb016bf53028dc22214122c8525bffc075b","tid":1128844,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"星期六去行山，睇雷達圖應該冇咁快落雨，一行八人去釣魚翁行山。<br />\n<br />\n路線：五塊田 &gt; 上洋山 &gt; 廟仔墩 &gt; 釣魚翁 &gt; 蝦山篤 &gt; 田下山 &gt; 大廟灣<br />\n<br />\n十點集合，鑽石山搭91去五塊田<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多即刻po圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PHFBno8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPHFBno8.jpg&h=de9dbdc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xacst39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXacst39.jpg&h=d8197901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上釣魚翁好難行，要用埋手先上到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XCPHpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XCPHpw.jpg&h=d4f6512a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好窄好高，雀仔軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpbEkaY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpbEkaY.jpg&h=c9f9466f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/28/135609_18689b329f962a3fc88f962ba2fdee32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F28%2F135609_18689b329f962a3fc88f962ba2fdee32.jpg&h=5d9fbe3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/28/135622_67978b1fcc3cb37d06b0dfdf2a67ec0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F28%2F135622_67978b1fcc3cb37d06b0dfdf2a67ec0e.jpg&h=a3684cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/28/135634_508ac3c298060d4de4dd6c478845030d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F28%2F135634_508ac3c298060d4de4dd6c478845030d.jpg&h=898ed2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊石幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZmTGyAp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmTGyAp.jpg&h=46b65a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全程行咗4粒鐘，冇補給站"},{"pid":"6a27cb0b7cb34f9ae8350cb0419819170004cf3b","tid":1128844,"uid":18170,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"5e09b49246b81fb0c86a13b9b0ad531fabce7fd9","tid":1128844,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"上過幾次啦, 個view ok既"},{"pid":"9913040b016bc292362ead046fd79d2efd040e4e","tid":1128844,"uid":176319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"感覺如何"},{"pid":"4fc9e557f5045147ab2ad7df16d7b76f9a1f8ce3","tid":1128844,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"9913040b016bc292362ead046fd79d2efd040e4e","tid":1128844,"uid":176319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"感覺如何"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T06:06:13.000Z","msg":"好大風，好攰，但個view唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261c2c84a0590b9af2ce3b568ab66b9fd7cac9a9","tid":1128844,"uid":176471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"